@*
    Sign Up Page, consists of Username, Email, Password, which constitutes a User.
    Database Call: REF: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/aspnet/web-api/overview/advanced/sending-html-form-data-part-1
    action="" call will be replaced in the future (if ever), to make a post call towards a proper address.
